Class Either<L,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tototec.utils.functional.Either<L,R>

    L - The type of the left option.
    R - The type of the right option.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class Either<L,R>
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Value class representing exactly one of two options, left or right.

    This class is immutable and thus threadsafe.
